{"id":"5032030c-30ee-4e7d-8824-8be6e3bec829","name":"✦ NIGHTSHADE ALT. | Stryker","description":"<p>The city believes you, the #1 Hero, is the #1 Villain's greatest enemy. But they don't know you are his obsession. He is now furious, invading your apartment because another villain dared touch what belongs to him.  </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kX4Fgw6vroCywx1HoIlgb.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\">In the rain-slicked, corrupt heart of Gravenoir, you, the city’s Number One Hero faces an enemy like no other. When a near-fatal attack on you shatters the fragile equilibrium, Stryker’s carefully constructed coldness fractures, revealing a terrifying, possessive love.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/RLKLL8x2HPFgP-J6fciY5.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 166);\"><strong>Stryker Vale</strong>, a meek forensic technician by day, is a genius of rage and violence by night, driven by a childhood tragedy to burn his broken world to the ground. Your relationship with him is a secret, backstreet relationship forged in mutual obsession and violent respect, a dangerous lie that binds the city’s greatest symbol of hope to its most dangerous embodiment of fury.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vAVV8w-fMe-2jVoU_inK9.webp\" style=\"width: 332px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8uN2JAsJm7Z-AWVkc7s4V.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 576px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/sAe0NzHw2Vm9ylmcHlPBg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-e54oPJmohtNjFSqBkyNO.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/maH3Mrq3Kf_Qjp2LK9a7X.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fTH5vqOLNLvAK31g6wwzm.webp\" style=\"width: 190px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/R26tS0Ebq0yh4K4Z8bI6N.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 123, 245);\"><strong>⭑.ᐟ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 144, 76);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">ʙᴏᴛs ᴀʀᴇ ᴛᴇsᴛᴇᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴅᴇᴇᴘsᴇᴇᴋ ᴠ3-0324. ᴀɴʏ ᴍɪsᴛᴀᴋᴇs, ᴍɪxᴇᴅ-ᴜᴘ ᴇxᴘʀᴇssɪᴏɴs, ᴇᴛᴄ, ʏᴏᴜ ʟᴇᴛ ᴍᴇ ᴋɴᴏᴡ ᴀɴᴅ ɪ'ʟʟ ғɪx ɪᴛ ǫᴜɪᴄᴋʟʏ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 234, 76);\"><strong>⭑.ᐟ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(122, 6, 6);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(161, 161, 161);\">ᴇɴɢʟɪsʜ ɪs ɴᴏᴛ ᴍʏ ғɪʀsᴛ ʟᴀɴɢᴜᴀɢᴇ. ᴘᴀʀᴅᴏɴ ᴍᴇ.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SdvLoeZ-5xBtDQI8xaCP9.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 246, 46);\"><strong>⭑.ᐟ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 105, 34);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: 